Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:28.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'll make dinner right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.45,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I told you I'd be back at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.35,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:37.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I've been feverish all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.91,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Dinner will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.52,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,You've been drawing manga, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:46.99,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(385,0)}Homemaker: \NKurasawa Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,{\a6}Someone from Tokiwa publishing is \Nreviewing it the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.79,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Will you hurry up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.01,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:55.20,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,0)}Kanae's husband:\N Kurasawa Yoshihito
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:01.40,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Don't make dinner tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.37,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I've been invited to general \Nmanager Tadokoro's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.25,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.29,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:10.56,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Can I go to the hospital tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.35,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:15.58,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I have no cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:22.69,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I give you cash every month, \Nand you're already out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:26.77,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Dumb woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.94,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Dear, you got a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:49.68,Bengoshi-Phone_Screen,Words on phone screen,0,0,0,,General Manager Tadokoro:\N Hey, hey, about tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.33,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text 1/4,0,0,0,,Score! I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.33,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text 2/4,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4FFF98&}I'm glad you're happy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.33,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text 3/4,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4FFF98&}She said dinner's ready, just a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:58.89,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text 4/4,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, about tomorrow's\N Spanish restaurant, I made\N the reservation!! Can't wait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.20,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text 1/4,0,0,0,,Score. I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.20,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text 2/4,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4FFF98&}I'm glad you're happy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.83,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text scrolling up from 1/4,0,0,0,,{\a9}I love you, too.\N\N Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:10.77,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Text from Tadokoro (in white background),0,0,0,,You chose your wife poorly (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.31,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'll be home late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.92,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, you're having dinner \Nwith general manager Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.46,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Yeah. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.20,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.53,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Give my regards to general \Nmanager Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.43,Bengoshi-Google,goodle search,0,0,0,,adultery divorce compensation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:37.31,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Filing divorce papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.18,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,It's usually around one million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:47.66,Default,Voice2,0,0,0,,The retainer fees, form preparation fees and\N contingency fee will total about a million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:51.42,Default,Voice2,0,0,0,,Many of people end up \Nbroke because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.54,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,End up broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.17,Default,Voice3,0,0,0,,If you'd still like to go\N through with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:59.00,Default,Voice3,0,0,0,,the retainer fees will be \N100,000 to 200,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'll have to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.00,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.30,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Kurasawa-san, I read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.73,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh. How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:20.85,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,To be honest, comparing this work to \Nlast year's newcomer award winner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.65,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,I just didn't feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.34,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.61,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,But, I'll have my senior \Neditor take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.03,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No, no. I'll redo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.56,Default,Server,0,0,0,,A refill for your beverage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.58,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Not for me, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.94,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.07,Default,Server,0,0,0,,A refill for your beverage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.90,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.77,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.70,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,You seemed to be much happier before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.53,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,{\a6}Before, when you encountered a guy like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.51,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(418,0)}Editor at Tokiwa Publishing: \NTabata Misato
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.51,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,{\a6}you would say, "Oh, I can \Nuse that in a manga!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.26,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,You were looking for material.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.58,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:05.38,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Well, you see... \NLately, my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.64,Default,Server,0,0,0,,A refill for your beverage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.50,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.49,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I don't want a refill \Nfor my beverage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.63,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,But can you pay me compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.19,Default,Server,0,0,0,,One order of compensation... Compenー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.57,Default,Server,0,0,0,,Compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.83,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Compensation for cheating on your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:26.94,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Four million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.60,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Four million...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.79,Default,Server,0,0,0,,You don't have to come to my restaurant\N and cause me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.18,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I sent you an affidavit to fill out the \Nother day, but haven't heard back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:42.41,Default,Server,0,0,0,,Is this the lowdown way \Nyou conduct business?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.68,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What an interesting thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.68,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You have a Twitter account, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:55.34,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,It's full of tweets \Ndegrading your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.87,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In terms of public and court opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.65,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,who would be viewed favorably?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.26,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The slandering cheater, \Nor the slandered wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.46,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Oh yes, and there will be further \Ncompensation you will be liable for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.25,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,1.5 million yen, for \Nwhich you will be billed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.16,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In total, that will be \N5.5 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.53,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.22,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kanae,0,0,0,,5.5 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.08,Default,Server,0,0,0,,How can I pay 5.5 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.01,Default,Server,0,0,0,,I can't afford that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.82,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,But you have this \Nrestaurant, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.50,Default,Server,0,0,0,,This is my precious restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.77,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,600 yen for one cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.34,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The sandwiches are dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:40.18,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The proprietor manages the restaurant \Nto fool around with young waitresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.53,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What a corrupt establishment this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:45.48,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Or, would you like for \Nthe court to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:48.11,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,All the details of your \Nadultery, what you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.98,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,when, and how, will all have to \Nbe reported in explicit detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:56.39,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,It might get drawn out for years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:06:00.75,Default,Server,0,0,0,,Please. Have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.67,Default,Server,0,0,0,,You see? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.12,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The one you should\N apologize to isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:10.97,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Can you guess who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.17,Default,Server,0,0,0,,My wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.28,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:30.79,Bengoshi-Title,Plaque,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N {\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:35.96,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Episode 1,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Epiosde 1 \NPlay the "Dumb Woman" and Get Compensated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.60,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.00,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You're an attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.51,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)}Attorney: \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.34,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.51,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}Do you need counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.07,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.17,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.28,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Can you follow me to my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.05,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But, I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.91,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:55.91,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kanae,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.08,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Hurry, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:04.82,Bengoshi-Office,Window words,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:04.82,Bengoshi-Office_Chinese,Window words,0,0,0,,Tiger's Lair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.07,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Hurry. It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.82,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.66,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.63,Bengoshi-Office_Wood,Plaque,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:13.62,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.06,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.01,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.74,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.97,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.69,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Want some sugar crisps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.97,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.38,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,So, are you the cheater \Nor the cheatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.68,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.54,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,That face says it's the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.40,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.24,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Well... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.63,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Maybe a victim of domestic violence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.58,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No, there's been no violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.92,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Oh, well. How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.50,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.92,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.55,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'll come back some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.02,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:18.52,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Because places like this charge you \Njust for listening to you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.16,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I've got no money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.33,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Consultation is free here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.63,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:28.80,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,The economy's tough, but he\N insists on acting on principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:31.33,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You've come to the right place, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.77,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei looks like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.77,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,but when it comes to practicing \Ndivorce-law, he's crazy good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.81,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.38,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:43.02,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,First step, fermentation, \Nhas been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,First step, fermentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:47.57,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei is into baking bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.69,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You were in such a hurry for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:56.19,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The first step of fermentation is the \Nmost important step in baking bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:09:00.49,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You could say this principle \Napplies to life, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.76,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,For relatives' weddings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.97,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,the first step should \Nbe fermentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.37,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.88,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.13,Bengoshi-Overlap,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.45,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.76,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.09,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.63,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My husband is cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.06,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.64,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Give me all the details, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:37.88,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.81,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm Kurasawa Kanae, 32 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.29,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm a stay-at-home wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:48.40,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My husband Yoshihito works for \Nan advertising agency. He's 39.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.16,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,We met eight years ago at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,then we got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:58.20,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I quit working immediately \Nafter I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.66,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm an aspiring \Nmanga illustrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I found out about the cheating \Nby reading his texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:08.68,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My husband has the woman's email \Naddress under a fake name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.06,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Didn't his cell phone have a lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.61,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,What a low-level coverup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:17.61,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kanae,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.71,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,He must really think you're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.31,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,"She'll never find out."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.58,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,"Even if she did, I could easily \Ntalk my way out of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:32.49,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,"Even in the worst case scenario,\N it wouldn't be a problem."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:35.96,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That's probably the extent \Nof what he thinks of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.06,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please, continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.46,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My husband is in charge \Nof all our finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:48.60,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He gives me an allowance of \N40,000 yen per month, and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.81,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,He's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:54.54,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Couples with husbands in full charge \Nof finances often go bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.10,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It's amazing you lasted eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:01.45,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,But, he's shelling out a fortune \Nfor his mistress, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:05.23,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,And it seems he's been calling me \N"that dumb woman" to his peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.62,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.50,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,An impoverished vocabulary \Nwhen it comes to insults.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.60,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Sensei. Tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.82,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.35,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:19.04,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,By the way... are all \Nof you lawyers, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:24.14,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I am a private investigator, \NUmemoto Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.14,Bengoshi-Kurumi_Card,Biz card,0,0,0,,Private Investigator: \N{\fs25\c&HD4C9D4&}Umemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.94,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Investigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.36,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,{\a6}Like a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:30.15,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,420)}Private Investigator:\N Umemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.57,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm intricately affiliated \Nwith this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.95,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'll be a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.82,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,I'm Shinozuka Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:42.32,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(490,490)}Temp: \NShinozuka Rina
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.18,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.62,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,{\a6}I help prepare documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.07,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm Toyama Yoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:46.49,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,0)}Office Landlord: \NToyama Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.49,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.05,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,The landlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.38,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,In other words, you have \Nnothing to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.01,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.22,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I owe this office a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:58.28,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You haven't paid rent yet,\N have you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.37,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I can pay you last month's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.34,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Let's start with the month before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:05.22,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You'd better take her on as a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.15,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,And when you get your fee, pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:13.01,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You owe me for \Ninvestigation expenses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.55,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,My temp job payment, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.32,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:23.94,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Do you really plan on getting a divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:26.70,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:29.12,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You're prepared to fight if you have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.14,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,With your husband, that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.98,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.18,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I want to divorce him and start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.01,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:42.55,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,For now, please return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.56,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.93,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.64,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Aren't you taking her on as a client?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.70,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I know I might be stepping \Nout of my bounds, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:54.73,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,This is of the most important decisions\N you'll make in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:58.43,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.74,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.15,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Why don't {\i1}you{\i0} think it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.13,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei, why don't you \Ntake her as a client?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.09,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You have no steady income as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.86,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.51,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Dinner's almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.33,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.85,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,It's our wedding anniversary next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.30,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'll be on a business trip, \Nso I can't celebrate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.96,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Wasn't this expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.74,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,You've been helping with our \Nbudget, so I could afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.74,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.47,Bengoshi-Phone_Screen,Words on cell,0,0,0,,General Manager Tadokoro:\N About next week's trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.80,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,White text1,0,0,0,,Was your wife happy? Wasn't that a good \Nchoice? I want a diamond for my birthday (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.80,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Green text2,0,0,0,,{\3c&H42FF6F&}OK you can expect that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.80,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,White text3,0,0,0,,Now we're set to really have \Na great trip next week!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:18.97,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Large text,0,0,0,,Was your wife happy? Wasn't that a good \Nchoice? I want diamond for my birthday (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.38,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Green text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H42FF6F&}She's a dumb woman after all. She's naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.21,Bengoshi-Phone_Chat,Green text (closeup),0,0,0,,{\a6}{\3c&H42FF6F&}She's a dumb woman after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.55,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm ready to fight my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.01,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I officially accept you as my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.94,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please follow my instructions\N for all of our upcoming actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.87,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.77,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.43,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.21,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:03.72,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,How much are the fees involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.59,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Shinozuka-san, please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.82,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Document preparation: 50,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:16.17,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Retainer fee: 300,000 yen when \Nnegotiating terms with other parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:20.19,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Fee contingent on success, \Ncall it a reward fee: 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.97,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.78,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,This particular case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.88,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,we will get about five million.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.44,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Five million?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:34.94,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,If you follow my instructions,\N I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.16,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What do you need me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:41.85,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I need you to continue playing \Nthe "dumb woman" for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.44,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Keep playing the dumb woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.20,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,and keep your husband's guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.63,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,For now, we let him swim freely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.69,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,and we gather evidence that \Nwill give us an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.08,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,We'll gather evidence regarding \Nwhen the infidelity began,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.89,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,the days and times of his \Ntrysts with his mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:02.25,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,and maybe even the number of times he's \Nhad physical relationships with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.23,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Physical relationships?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:08.41,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What we need is reliable evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.58,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Photos of him cheating, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.68,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,How are you going to \Nacquire such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.24,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Ye of little faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:21.00,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on techniques \NI learned from the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,The CIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.61,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,From this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:33.54,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,"Iron Spy Woman, Marilyn" \NSeason 2, episode 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.71,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,If you want to learn about the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.08,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,first you have to know their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.42,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:45.73,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.56,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Cars are filled with information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.62,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,First, the GPS history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:58.76,Bengoshi-GPS2,GPS history,0,0,0,,{\a5}History Search
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:58.76,Bengoshi-GPS,GPS history,0,0,0,,Diver Street 07 Jan 14 \NShinagawa Royal Hotel 07 Jan 14 \NSky Bridge 05 Jan 14 \NMinami Yurakucho 23 Dec 13 \NC'est bonjour Bar 14 Dec 13\NGrand Hills 14 Dec 13 \NKaruizawa Golf Club 07 Dec 13 \NKaruizawa Garden Hotel 07 Dec 13 \NYoyogi Station 07 Dec 13\N Roppongi Sky Tower 07 Dec 13
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.20,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Kurumi,0,0,0,,After you gather the GPS history,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.47,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,don't forget to attach the GPS tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:11.71,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Once we pinpoint their date \Nlocation from tracker data...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.91,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,We storm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.31,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We storm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.12,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.56,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.23,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\a3}Yoshihito's subordinate: \NAikawa Shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.23,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.16,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,What a wasted opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.81,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Why didn't you snap the picture \Nas they went into the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.73,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I just couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.17,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.06,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:17.14,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I understand how you must feel. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.46,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Kanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.82,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You did decide to go through \Nwith the divorce, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:27.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:30.15,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,And from that moment onward,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.31,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,that your husband would \Nbecome a total stranger to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.28,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,A person with whom you\N would not grow old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:41.29,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,And you would be able to \Nseparate yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.20,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,from this stranger, \Na person who infuriates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:49.12,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,And you'll be able to get a lot of money\N from that total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:52.25,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Everything you see is \Ngoing to turn into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.77,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Can you hear the fanfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:02.57,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,Defeat your enemies \Nwith a heart of lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.62,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,These are perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:11.42,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,The mistress is Aikawa Shiori, \Na subordinate at my husband's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.56,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,The infidelity began \Nlast year in February.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:18.73,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,As to the physical relationships, \NI have confirmed at least 24 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:21.54,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,It must have been hard for you \Nto gather that much information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.78,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But, when I think of him\N as a total stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I think to myself,\N"This is material for manga."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:31.60,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Actually, I found myself \Nhaving fun at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.11,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I feel like a spy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.21,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:39.88,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Your actions were the most \Nelementary of the elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.93,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It'll take you another 15 years of\Nexperience to reach Marilyn's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.42,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Well, let's move \Non to the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.81,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.93,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,This time, I want you to cheer him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.53,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.86,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I want you to cheer on \NYoshihito-san's love affair...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.90,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,with all your might.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.92,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'll be late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.85,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,General Manager Tadokoro \Nis having me over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.22,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.90,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Have a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:13.06,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.23,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You're going out for drinks, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.03,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You should have the \Nbest time you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.43,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.60,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.53,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.00,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.18,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.55,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,May I have a moment of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:44.39,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We're searching for a lovely couple\N to be wedding-ring models.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.82,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,She called us a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.63,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.09,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Please, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.83,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Please, come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.86,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.80,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,They're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.77,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,We're actually not married yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.24,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.54,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It's just you two seemed \Nso suited for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:06.01,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,But, isn't your wedding \Nfast approaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:06.81,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.48,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.11,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I speak from much experience \Nin this line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.62,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.99,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We're currently having a newlyweds campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:19.26,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We're giving discounts \Nfor wedding rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.93,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.83,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'm a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:26.63,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,What a kind husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.93,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Whoops, jumped the gun \Non the "husband" part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.87,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,But I sense the start of a happy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:34.11,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You make me envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:39.42,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Envious! Envious! Envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:44.85,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Excuse me, please mind our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:50.22,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Those two are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.16,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.91,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,If they were just fooling around,  \Nthey'd cringe at the word "marriage."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:58.20,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,But Yoshihito-san is \Nbehaving like a newlywed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.90,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,He even bought her a wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.27,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.90,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,But, now the ball's in our court.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:08.34,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.84,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,If he's serious about marrying her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:14.08,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,he'll be willing to pay \Nhighly to get a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:15.98,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:18.92,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Also, because we've given \Nthem the encouragement,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.52,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,their love affair is at high tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:26.16,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Yoshihito-san may ask you\N for a divorce himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:30.93,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,And that will be our best chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.13,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:33.06,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:39.09,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I have something important \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.71,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.15,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'm in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:51.12,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:57.59,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I want to marry her eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:07.17,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Of course I'll wait \Nuntil you're ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.43,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:12.04,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Let's get divorced. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:13.71,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:16.71,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's not an eventual thing, \Nyou've already decided, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:19.14,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:25.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Will you let me draft \Nthe divorce papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:28.89,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:35.19,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}By using his guilty \Nconscience to our advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:38.30,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}he will let you draft \Nthe divorce papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:45.24,Bengoshi-Divorce_Papers,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(460,460)}Divorce Papers \N{\c&HEAEAF2&}Contracts regarding the compensation fee, division of assets,\N and other financial settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:42.80,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}Divorce papers specify all financial settlements \Nafter the divorce is finalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:46.07,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}We will draft it to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:49.97,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That's why you wanted me\N to cheer on their affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:53.14,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Now, the compensation you desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:54.31,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,How much should we make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.95,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Is there some kind of standard for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:01.85,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Actually, there's a site that \Nwill do the calculations for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:06.29,Bengoshi-Compensation_Calculator,Web site,0,0,0,,Divorce Compensation \NNumber of years married: 8-under 9 years\NOffending spouse's income: 5 million-under 6 million yen \NDuration of infidelity: 1-under 2 years\NPhysical relations: More than 20 times\NStatus of marriage: Not on good terms\N{\c&H574597&}Divorce Compensation: {\c&H5E5850&}4,116,720 yen\N\N{\c&H64574B&}Calculate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.22,0:24:04.66,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,His age, years of marriage, \Nduration of infidelity,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.29,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,number of of physical relationships...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:09.16,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,By entering the data...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:10.46,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Within 2 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:11.13,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.63,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,It comes out to 4,116,620 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:14.83,Bengoshi-Compensation_Calculator,Web site,0,0,0,,Number of times of illicit affair: Over 20 times\NRegarding marriage relationship: Not on good terms\N {\c&H574597&}Divorce Compensation: {\c&H5E5850&}4,116,720 yen\N\N{\c&H64574B&}Calculate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.63,0:24:14.83,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:17.80,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}The calculated sum is highly reflective \Nof the duration of the affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:24.68,Bengoshi-Divorce_Papers,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}Compensation Calculation Site: \N{\c&HF8F5FA&}Calculations are based on length of illicit love affair, annual income,\Nthe number of physical relationships, and other factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:21.17,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}and number of times of \Nphysical relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.84,0:24:25.48,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's quite a sum. But, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:28.58,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That would be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:34.19,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In that case, the compensation we'll \Ndemand of your husband will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.19,0:24:35.72,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Paper,0,0,0,,{\b1}Divorce Agreement{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.22,0:24:37.46,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Six million?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.46,0:24:38.86,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Words,0,0,0,,{\fs25}I agree to pay six million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.46,0:24:40.93,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes. It was calculated \Nat a specialist's site.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.23,0:24:45.83,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,First, you present him \Nwith a higher figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.83,0:24:47.60,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.60,0:24:49.13,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I don't have that kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:50.77,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Then, you move on to the discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.77,0:24:54.04,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,The figures are estimates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.04,0:24:57.24,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Of course you have to figure \Nliving expenses with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.91,0:25:00.11,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.81,0:25:01.88,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:03.75,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,When he lets down his guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.75,0:25:05.05,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,you show him a convenient payment plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.05,0:25:07.29,Bengoshi-Payment_Plan,Paper,0,0,0,,5 Million Yen{\c&H494468&} [5 Year Payment Plan]\N 60 installments
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.05,0:25:07.29,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I can agree to a five-year payment plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.29,0:25:11.59,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You'll only have to pay \N 83,300 yen per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.59,0:25:15.89,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,83,300 yen a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.13,0:25:20.03,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I guess that'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.97,0:25:24.24,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Paper,0,0,0,,{\fs30}5 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.24,0:25:26.30,Bengoshi-Signatures,Paper,0,0,0,,Kurasawa Yoshihito \N Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.70,0:25:26.30,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.30,0:25:31.58,Default,All,0,0,0,,Congratulations! You got the compensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.48,0:25:34.81,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.88,0:25:40.85,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.29,0:25:44.12,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,It's far better.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.12,0:25:46.39,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,I'll show it to my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.86,0:25:49.93,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,You don't even have to show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.53,0:25:57.07,Bengoshi-Credits_Waitress,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,420)}Cafe waitress: \NMizutani Sara
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.70,0:25:55.90,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,This manga will definitely \Nget syndication.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:57.94,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.51,0:26:06.04,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.78,0:26:08.85,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I am never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.05,0:26:11.35,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.88,0:26:13.35,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.89,0:26:15.25,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:19.92,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,Just a waitress at the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.92,0:26:22.19,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,Here's your iced coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.59,0:26:24.80,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But, I ordered a hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:27.23,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,Oh! I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.23,0:26:29.50,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I'll bring it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.60,0:26:34.74,Bengoshi-Outside_Plaque,Plaque,0,0,0,,Kurasawa
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.02,0:26:49.22,Bengoshi-Editor_Text,Cell,0,0,0,,Tabata Misato\NToday's Manuscript\N\NMy superiors loved it!\N Monthly Man-day will run it\N as a syndication next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.23,0:27:00.50,Bengoshi-Apartment_Rentals,Cell,0,0,0,,Apartment Rentals
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.23,0:27:00.50,Bengoshi-Apartment_Rentals_Sancha,Cell,0,0,0,,Sangen-jaya Station
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.23,0:27:01.57,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Sancha's a nice area.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.20,0:27:04.80,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,This one has a walk-in closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:09.47,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Can we wait on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.68,0:27:12.94,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.85,0:27:16.51,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,The divorce settlement is expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.51,0:27:18.52,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Compensation and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:21.52,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,How much is the compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:22.95,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.89,0:27:25.09,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,about five million.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.09,0:27:26.72,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Five million?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.53,0:27:31.23,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Can't you do something about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.10,0:27:34.13,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I've already given my signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.44,0:27:41.87,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.87,0:27:44.58,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.89,0:27:57.92,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,She sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.33,0:28:03.23,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Are you Kurasawa Yoshihito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.66,0:28:04.90,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.23,0:28:08.20,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I'm Kanae-san's legal representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.63,0:28:11.44,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,My name is Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:13.57,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Card,Biz card,0,0,0,,Attorney: \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.34,0:28:16.41,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,A lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.82,0:28:18.68,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.01,0:28:22.28,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,but I've got the official divorce \Nagreement document for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.72,0:28:31.89,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.96,0:28:35.26,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I cannot stick to this agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.22,0:28:36.96,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:39.93,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,How could I pay compensation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:42.43,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,We've got living expenses to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.43,0:28:43.57,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.20,0:28:47.84,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,However, you have already consented.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.54,0:28:50.71,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I admit to my infidelity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.24,0:28:55.75,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,But, Kanae and I were already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.02,0:29:04.36,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I was miserable for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.76,0:29:08.03,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,day after day, without \Nany excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.06,0:29:12.86,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I started hating myself \Nfor growing old like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.83,0:29:17.34,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Things changed when I met Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:20.47,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,It was just for laughs at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.21,0:29:24.05,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,But when I was with Shiori,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.54,0:29:28.46,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I felt like a man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.61,0:29:32.28,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Then things got serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.82,0:29:36.89,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,You're a man, too. Can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.86,0:29:40.96,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.19,0:29:44.90,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.67,0:29:53.34,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Because I'm not a fool who \Nwould cheat on my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.25,0:29:58.44,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.85,0:30:04.63,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I know it's none of my business, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.95,0:30:08.12,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Before you set your life straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.89,0:30:13.69,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,don't you have something \Nyou need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.60,0:30:18.40,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.40,0:30:32.81,Bengoshi-Tokiwa_Publishers,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.81,0:30:31.84,Bengoshi-Tokiwa_Publishers,Wall,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Publishers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.72,0:30:40.32,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,This is my superior, Ueki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.55,0:30:43.96,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,I'm Ueki, chief editor of \NMonthly Man-day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.49,0:30:46.12,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.56,0:30:48.39,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.63,0:30:52.76,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I have made some modifications \Nto the previous manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.48,0:30:57.74,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.13,0:30:59.80,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,Concerning the syndication...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.38,0:31:02.04,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,it's been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.54,0:31:05.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What was wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.14,0:31:06.21,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I can change it all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.21,0:31:09.28,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,That's not the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.35,0:31:13.02,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Our superiors put a stop on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.42,0:31:14.52,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.52,0:31:19.89,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,Our advertising sponsor \Nput in their word...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.89,0:31:23.63,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,they are our sponsor, \Nso it's out of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.57,0:31:26.43,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.18,0:31:40.35,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.71,0:31:46.32,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My syndication by Tokiwa Publishers\N was canceled today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.22,0:31:49.59,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.95,0:31:55.63,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Our advertising agency directs many \Nof our clients to Tokiwa Publishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.06,0:32:00.10,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,We also have long-term relationships \Nwith many other major sponsors as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.17,0:32:05.54,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I think it's going to be very difficult \Nfor you to make a living in this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.74,0:32:08.31,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.31,0:32:09.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You're behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.64,0:32:15.85,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Could you rethink the compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.40,0:32:17.38,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.38,0:32:18.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That was dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.82,0:32:21.32,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me about dirty tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.99,0:32:25.16,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,That lanky-looking lawyer \Nfed you ideas, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.69,0:32:27.79,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,He's out to gouge me, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.79,0:32:30.49,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Besides, this is a matter \Nbetween husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:35.17,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Shouldn't it be the \Ntwo of us who decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.19,0:32:57.32,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Um, Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.32,0:32:58.62,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,May I have a little of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.44,0:33:00.73,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Kanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.73,0:33:01.69,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.03,0:33:03.30,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.00,0:33:09.10,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I want to rewrite the divorce agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.83,0:33:10.74,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.54,0:33:14.41,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I want to lessen the compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.57,0:33:18.94,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Did your husband say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.14,0:33:25.52,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I know it's none of my business, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.19,0:33:30.22,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I cannot acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.89,0:33:36.80,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But this is a matter between us,\N as husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.80,0:33:38.39,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,No, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.24,0:33:40.97,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,When your husband had the affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.40,0:33:45.77,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,he rejected the wholesome marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:49.27,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,From that moment on,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.41,0:33:54.65,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,the two of you became \Nperpetrator and victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.95,0:34:02.55,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Adultery is viewed as \Nmalicious intent by the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.89,0:34:10.32,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I view it as no different from a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.80,0:34:18.34,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The adulterer should be duly penalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.24,0:34:29.65,OfficeSign,Yukio,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.65,0:34:31.05,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.05,0:34:31.62,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.61,0:34:34.56,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,What happened with the compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.10,0:34:36.96,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.96,0:34:40.26,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I have no intention of paying \Nsuch a ridiculous sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:43.53,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.53,0:34:46.70,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'm not some domestic simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.70,0:34:49.43,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I'm a survivor of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.70,0:34:52.17,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,I don't take things lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.24,0:34:55.51,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.21,0:35:01.53,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.32,0:35:11.02,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,The compensation has been modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.69,0:35:16.46,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Now you and I can start \Nliving our new lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.66,0:35:19.36,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Paper,0,0,0,,{\3c&H88A2AB&}Divorce Agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.36,0:35:21.23,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Paper,0,0,0,,{\fs30\3c&HB0B7C5&}10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:20.96,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Ten million?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.67,0:35:23.30,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.30,0:35:25.57,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Regarding that, let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.68,0:35:30.74,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.74,0:35:32.01,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,We've already met.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.88,0:35:37.41,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,First of all, regarding: "Ten million? \NWhat's the meaning of this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.95,0:35:40.89,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Let me answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.89,0:35:46.11,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,First of all, compensation is \Nmeasured by psychological duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.69,0:35:51.56,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Notwithstanding, by continuing to see\Nyour partner in infidelity...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.30,0:35:54.12,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,and bringing her into your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.20,0:36:02.37,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Kanae-san's psychological duress has \Ndoubled since you made the agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.21,0:36:04.91,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,That will cost two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:10.42,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You have also acted to obstruct \NKanae-san's profession as manga illustrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.88,0:36:12.92,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The compensation for \Nthat will be two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.49,0:36:16.89,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In total, the sum is now ten million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.89,0:36:19.66,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Are you joking? I don't \Nhave ten million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.93,0:36:22.43,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.16,0:36:29.20,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,But, it was Kurasawa Yoshihito-san, \Nemployee of the electronic advertising agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.62,0:36:35.06,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,who acted to cancel Kanae-san's \Nsyndication at the publishing company.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.14,0:36:38.10,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I will be reporting \Nthis to your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.10,0:36:39.34,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.34,0:36:40.78,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,Please don't involve the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.78,0:36:44.52,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In that case, will you make the payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.45,0:36:48.15,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.01,0:36:50.32,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.19,0:36:54.03,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,we will see you in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.99,0:36:58.87,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,And I will fight you, for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.84,0:37:01.99,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,even decades, however long \Nit takes, to make you pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.47,0:37:10.81,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You should remember this for the next \Ntime you agree to a compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.74,0:37:15.31,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,There is something an \Nadulterer must first do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.98,0:37:17.38,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,That is to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.58,0:37:21.09,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The second thing to do, is apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.95,0:37:24.02,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The third thing to do is likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.03,0:37:28.09,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,You will have to keep on apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.66,0:37:33.81,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,And yet, notwithstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:38.34,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,you haven't asked Kanae-san's \Nforgiveness, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.91,0:37:45.15,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I have no intention of lessening the \Ncompensation for a person like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.23,0:37:48.58,Default,Yoshihito,0,0,0,,But still, this sum is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.75,0:37:54.52,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,August 17th, Karuizawa Hotel,\N Junior Suite, one night, 32,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:59.39,Bengoshi-Expense_List,Sheets,0,0,0,,Expense List of Illicit Affair
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.09,0:37:58.59,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,October 3rd, Spain \NRestaurant, 13,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.59,0:38:03.43,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,November 9th, Hokkaido Crab \NBuffet Tour, 75,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.00,0:38:06.90,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Just from what we know about, in six months,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.90,0:38:10.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,you've spent over one million \Nyen for Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:15.57,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Considering that, the sum isn't \Nimpossible for you to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.61,0:38:21.50,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,To this day, I haven't had any client \Nwhose research was more thorough...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.78,0:38:24.81,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I almost wish she'd \Ncome work at my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.82,0:38:30.59,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In contrast, to this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.99,0:38:33.79,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I haven't met anyone come up with a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.16,0:38:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,more stupid scheme to \Nlessen the compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.57,0:38:41.57,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Of all the men I have ever met...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.20,0:38:48.87,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,you are a "dumb man" \Nof the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.62,0:39:01.81,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.67,0:39:06.12,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,As to the rest, talk it \Nover at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.71,0:39:25.78,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.27,0:39:31.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My husband consented.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.84,0:39:35.92,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He said he'll pay ten million yen \Nin a five-year payment plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.70,0:39:38.06,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.06,0:39:41.56,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Usually when it goes to court,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.56,0:39:46.93,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,the court generally agrees \Non one to two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.42,0:39:48.17,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.87,0:39:50.79,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,In order for you to have gotten \Nthe high compensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.10,0:39:54.07,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,the agreement phase was critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.91,0:39:57.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.98,0:40:00.66,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What have you got planned for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.18,0:40:04.02,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My current apartment is costly,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.02,0:40:07.25,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,so I'm going to find \Nanother place to rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.49,0:40:09.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.76,0:40:13.76,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You have been truly good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.19,0:40:15.09,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.92,0:40:20.13,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.17,0:40:27.21,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Kanae-san's a different person \Nfrom when she first walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.81,0:40:31.48,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,But tougher battles are yet \Nto be fought. Right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.00,0:40:35.91,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.25,0:40:37.67,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,The bread is baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.89,0:41:17.86,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Office_Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.89,0:41:20.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.83,0:41:22.33,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Kanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.90,0:41:24.46,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Are you in trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.46,0:41:25.46,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.60,0:41:28.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I have a different request today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.96,0:41:31.51,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,A different request?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.77,0:41:37.77,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Would you let me work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.61,0:41:39.48,Default,Yukio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.21,0:41:42.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,My manga is about to get syndicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.61,0:41:44.78,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.18,0:41:46.49,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.95,0:41:51.32,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,This main character looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.49,0:41:53.29,Bengoshi-Bubble,Bubble,0,0,0,,{\3c&HDFE9D9&}You will pay\N the compensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.12,0:41:53.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.36,0:41:55.69,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,It looks like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.69,0:41:57.86,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,Especially the goofy look.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.86,0:42:00.20,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,He's an attorney specializing \Nin divorce compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.20,0:42:04.17,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I thought if I worked here, \NI'd always have material...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.17,0:42:06.87,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,Well, you might find material,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.87,0:42:09.21,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,but lawyers must keep \Nclient confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.21,0:42:11.68,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll\N fictionalize those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.91,0:42:15.15,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,You did say, Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.15,0:42:18.42,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,that you would want me \Nto work at your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.42,0:42:21.15,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,That was a figure of speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.15,0:42:22.39,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.99,0:42:24.72,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You're hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.72,0:42:25.89,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.89,0:42:28.36,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,Toyama-san, you're just the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.93,0:42:32.30,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,How many months' rent \Ndo you think you owe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.30,0:42:36.54,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,She can advertise your firm \Nin that manga, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.80,0:42:37.94,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.87,0:42:42.23,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,Under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.71,0:42:43.71,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.20,0:42:49.31,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,This character...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.62,0:42:52.35,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,can't you make him look more handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.29,0:43:05.89,Bengoshi-Next_Episode,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,310)}Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.79,0:42:56.05,Default,Group,0,0,0,,Double adultery!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.05,0:42:57.66,Bengoshi-Top,Voice,0,0,0,,I can't forgive my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.27,0:43:03.49,Bengoshi-Double_Adultery,Caption,0,0,0,,Husband's {\c&HB657D3&}double adultery!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.80,0:43:00.69,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,Compensation can be collected \Nfrom the mistress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.07,0:43:03.49,Bengoshi-Mistress_Compensation,Caption,0,0,0,,Collect compensation {\c&HE7D7C6&}from the mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.83,0:43:02.26,Bengoshi-Top,Woman,0,0,0,,I was forced to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.26,0:43:03.50,Bengoshi-Top,Woman,0,0,0,,And he raped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.72,0:43:05.56,Bengoshi-Top,Yukio,0,0,0,,Look forward to the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.81,0:43:08.07,Bengoshi-Top,Judge,0,0,0,,The court has decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.05,0:44:06.05,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,0)}This drama is a work of fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.05,0:44:08.05,Bengoshi-Fiction,,0,0,0,,

